node.text:
Spotting sea snakes with @brodiemoss 😮 Get your photos posted in our account, apply for a feature visiting globefever.com 👉🏼 the link is in our bio: @globefever 

“Sea snakes normally avoid humans but this time of year they become very active, sexually frustrated and potentially aggressive as they search for a mate 🐍 like this old fella who appeared from the ocean floor and followed me around on my paddle board before disappearing 😅”

What would you do in this situation? 😱

📽 @brodiemoss
📍Australia

Switzerland Villages Fairytale!🏡 Apply for a feature following the link in our bio and we will publish your photos in our account: @globefever 

Which location is your favorite from 1 - 10?😍 

Locations and Videos:
1. #Rosenlaui @world.from.my.eyes
2. #Schwytz @doounias
3. #Brienz @sennarelax
4. #SwissAlps @swissaround_
5. #Foroglio #Ticino @emrije.a
6. #Lungern @amir_asani13
7. #Uri @sennarelax
8. #Oberwald @doounias
9. #Hasliberg @syifa_in_switzerland
10. #Seerenbachfälle @swissaround_
